<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. Results of four variants of NC-clustering: NC-Ward (hierarchical, tree shown), NC-part. hclust (hierarchical), NC-part. kmeans (iterative vector-quantisation), NC-NMDS (non-metric scaling); 21 nest samples of Plagiolepis schmitzii (grey bars) and of 20 nest samples of Pl. atlantis (black bars). Outliers in NC-part. hclust are given by the white gap." , "Figure 4. Dorsal aspect of a worker of Plagiolepis schmitzii (image from AntWeb 2020: CASENT 0906252, photographer E. Ortega)." , "Figure 2. Head of a worker of Plagiolepis schmitzii (image from AntWeb, 2020: CASENT 0906252, photographer E. Ortega)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/455223" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/455222" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/455220" .

